If you are running MediaThread on something other than 64bit linux, then do the
following:

1. Visit http://www.egenix.com/products/python/mxBase/ and download the appropriate 3.1.3
file.
2. unzip the file, cd into the directory 
3. run:
  python setup.py bdist_egg
4. copy the dist/egenix_mx_base-3.1.3* file to this directory (mediathread/requirements/eggs)

